<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM1.2">
<l>veḷḷainuṇ maṇaṟkoṇṭu teruvaṇintu veḷvaraip pataṉmuṉṉan tuṟaipaṭintu</l>
<l>muḷḷumil lāccuḷḷi yerimaṭuttu muyaṉṟuṉṉai nōṟkiṉṟēṉ kāmatēvā</l>
<l>kaḷḷaviḻ pūṅkaṇai toṭuttukkoṇṭu kaṭalvaṇṇa ṉeṉpatōr pēreḻutip</l>
<l>puḷḷiṉai vāypiḷan tāṉeṉpatō rilakkiṉiṟ pukaveṉṉai yeykiṟṟiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having adorned the streets with fine white sand, bathed in the ghats before dawn breaks,</l>
<l>Kindled fire with thornless dry twigs, I practise austerities for you,</l>
<l rend="indent">exerting myself, O Kāmadeva!</l>
<l>Fixing a honey-dripping flower arrow, writing the unique name</l>
<l rend="indent">‘ocean sea-hued [Lord]’ [on it],</l>
<l>Will you be able to discharge me so that [I] enter that singular Target</l>
<l rend="indent">that is [the Lord] who split open the bird’s mouth?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
